{"tid":1015667,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被撤居留權　華富商向澳政黨追捐款","createTime":"2019-02-10T08:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T13:59:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4f6f0a2fe200d75b6a3f54b6be08e835d954ef","tid":1015667,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:00:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190210/20609718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190210%2F20609718&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BNAsgxU2M8QNPxyQAqp636I%3D&h=8036e0fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190210%2F20609718&h=00c0d883\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190210/20609718</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年02月10日 <br />\n<br />\n被撤居留權　華富商向澳政黨追捐款<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190210/large/a1005a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190210%2Flarge%2Fa1005a.gif&h=97122b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃向墨要求澳洲政黨歸還捐款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國富商黃向墨涉干預澳洲內政被澳洲撤銷永久居留權後，向澳洲政府進行大反擊，批評澳洲政府實行種族主義；不點名要求澳洲政黨退還捐款，金額或涉270萬澳元（約1,512萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱已回港定居「安心快樂」<br />\n<br />\n黃向墨前日在澳洲華人網站億億網發表聲明，強調沒有觸犯任何澳洲法律、法規，指他所有政治捐款都是政黨和政治人物的懇求而捐贈的，並非他主動捐獻，呼籲若政黨及政治人物認為他們主動索取的捐款是不合適的，應當退還。黃承諾，對方不用支付利息；收到退款後，將把這些捐款改捐慈善機構。據報，自由黨及工黨等澳洲政黨均收過黃的政治捐款。<br />\n<br />\n黃又稱，在澳洲安全情報組織ASIO的相關文件，質疑他在中國的商業關係、親屬關係等可能對澳洲構成威脅，黃暗批澳洲指控十分荒謬。他指中國也有許多澳洲企業，其投資應該遠大於黃在澳的投資，若據此懷疑他們更易被中國政府操縱，一定是荒謬的。黃指出，澳洲玉湖集團去年已完成接班工作，他本人亦回到香港定居，安心快樂；揚言會在合適的時間以合適的身份訪澳。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲《悉尼先驅晨報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n騰訊擬擲11億入股「美版連登」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n中美明日北京會談　傳美擬押後死線"},{"pid":"7baaba89328c899719956fc3a6c1a32beb022487","tid":1015667,"uid":141151,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:04:33.000Z","msg":"On9仔  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDonation 定義就係完全不問回報<br />\n仲想問人拎返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efdb209001eb04d6e0e42896953e0ebe49ab936f","tid":1015667,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"ccc"},{"pid":"a54a963497f79e4d91b25c16712e92379c8c835c","tid":1015667,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:09:57.000Z","msg":"揚言會在合適的時間以合適的身份訪澳。<br />\n拍左片話不自殺未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150c695cd26ad0ba41c7cebcfddac0209c35568c","tid":1015667,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:11:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f739cbc252575cf971110019ff51bb51ade76c8","tid":1015667,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7baaba89328c899719956fc3a6c1a32beb022487","tid":1015667,"uid":141151,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:04:33.000Z","msg":"On9仔  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDonation 定義就係完全不問回報<br />\n仲想問人拎返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:13:31.000Z","msg":"sorry中國人唔識英文"},{"pid":"1e4bcd8c30483191a1c89f913175d80625dd1b5a","tid":